    <summary>Interface for nVidia Optimus</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            This is a graphical user interface for Laptops with nVidia Optimus Technology (eg. switchable Graphics).
        </p>
        <p>
            This application is most useful on older nvidia GPUs featuring the Pascal micro architecture like GTX 10
            series
            or older as these lack proper power management using the proprietary nvidia driver. OptimusUI requires a
            supported prime tool like SUSEPrime, nvidia-prime, fedora-prime-select or nvidia-prime-select to be
            installed on the host system.
        </p>
    </description>

